"P(orange)",
"T",
"P(lemon)",
"F",
"P(true)",
"F",
"P(false)",
"T"
);

$tf ->choose(4);

BEGIN_TEXT
$PAR

Let P(x) be the statement $LQ the word x contains the letter `a'
$RQ. What are the truth values of the following? $BR
\{ $tf -> print_q \}
$PAR
END_TEXT

